oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmie Rodgers Country Music Hall of Fame Plaque: Smaller Photo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing; Rodgers, Jimmie, 1897-1933;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet featuring a photograph of Jimmie Rodgers' Country Music Hall of Fame plaque. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
